            <h1 class="w-[90%] xl:w-[45vw] text-[#001854] font-inter not-italic font-bold text-[3rem] md:text-[4rem] xl:text-[5.5rem] leading-[3.3rem] md:leading-[5rem] select-none text-center xl:text-start">Спасете бъдещето чрез силата на <span class="inline bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-center bg-cover bg-[url('../img/ai-gradient.png')]">Изкуствения Интелект</span>.</h1>
            <button @onclick="DownloadFileFromURL" class="xl:h-[6vw] w-1/2 mt-[10%] bg-gradient-to-r from-[#61B3FF] to-[#8321FF] rounded-[93px] font-inter not-italic font-extrabold text-[4.5vw] xl:text-[2.5vw] text-[#FFFFFF]">
            Започни сега
                <svg class="inline pl-[1vw] w-[2vw]" width="30" height="45" viewBox="0 0 30 45" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
